items.desc: "AnimeFeet", the Animated Foot Scenes Wiki includes many graphical mediums. We focus on all types of characters with an encyclopedic scope, hoping to appeal to a wider audience. We strive to capture, collect and store the most interesting foot scenes available to the watchers of anime and cartoons, and to the readers of manga and comic books.
